### Get author list with filter

GET http://localhost:1234/authors?age=lt:50&name=автор&is_alive=true&sort_by=age&sort_order=asc
Content-Type: application/json

### Get author page 1
GET http://localhost:1234/authors?limit=5
Content-Type: application/json

### Get author page 2
GET http://localhost:1234/authors?limit=5&ptoken=?
Content-Type: application/json

### Get author list with sorting

GET http://localhost:1234/authors?sort_by=age&sort_order=desc
Content-Type: application/json

